short_summary: Service truck cap and other equipment, incl. installation located in Valcartier, Qu. Canada
description: Bid solicitation cancels and supersedes previous bid solicitation number W7701-237704 dated  28-09-2022 with a closing of 27-10-2022 at 2:00p.m. \\'A debriefing or feedback session will be provided upon request to bidders/offerors/suppliers who bid on the previous solicitation. All required supporting documentation and bid submission must be submitted at the latest by 2 PM EST on 13,12,2022. All bids submitted after 2 PM EST will result in the bid being declared non-responsive. PWGSC, on behalf of THE DEPARTMENT OF NATIONAL DEFENCE, DRDC, DEFENCE RESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT CANADA – VALCARTIER RESEARCH CENTRE is issuing this REQUEST FOR PROPOSAL (RFP) for the acquisition of a SERVICE TRUCK CAP AND OTHER EQUIPMENT including INSTALLATION located in Valcartier, Qu. Canada, as detailed in Annex A.
